Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說所有萌文化都從秋葉原消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡倫…岡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎之穴和安利美特都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mandarake和Gamers呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢 岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉原不可能有那些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才會繞路去中野買同人志嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理 你是在MayQueen打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MayQueen？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MayQueen喵喵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出要把萌文化引進秋葉原的…是菲利斯喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把否定這件事的D-MAIL發送到了過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅一封簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整條街居然被完全改變了
